233
00:17:53,630 --> 00:17:55,950
Get out! Get out!

234
00:17:55,950 --> 00:17:57,800
Seriously!

235
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,950
Do you hate me that much?

236
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:06,220
You hated everything?

237
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:08,440
But I...

238
00:18:09,410 --> 00:18:11,010
I loved you!

239
00:18:11,010 --> 00:18:12,660
Shut up!

240
00:18:12,660 --> 00:18:14,820
- So Yeong, take him with you. 
 - Okay.

241
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:17,620
You worked hard!

242
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:24,070
Team Leader, these are some images I've picked out.

243
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:29,620
Okay, and you've spoken with the visual merchandising department regarding The Hills store?

244
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:34,270
Yes. They said that they would get an interior plan together after seeing the scale and location of the store.

245
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:36,200
Tomorrow, I will be going directly to The Hills to work.

246
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:38,000
Okay.

247
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:40,290
Are you not going home, Team Leader?

248
00:18:40,290 --> 00:18:42,190
I will a little later.

249
00:18:43,380 --> 00:18:46,790
It's really nice working with you.

250
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:50,370
Thank you for making it so that I'm able to retain my pride.

251
00:18:51,090 --> 00:18:52,510
We all did it together.

252
00:18:52,510 --> 00:18:57,990
As for me, I will help more and more for next season and the one after that.

253
00:18:57,990 --> 00:19:01,510
- All right, let's do that. 
 - Okay.

254
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:03,910
Then, see you tomorrow.

